{"title":"窗口","authors":["牛汉"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个从朝鲜前线回来的老乡说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在清川江两岸的村庄里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来也不敢从窗口走过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为了心爱的人们打开的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是为了祖国打开的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前，在窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖母缝着衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈在这里望着爸爸从田野回来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青人唱着歌从窗前走过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹进来，阳光照进来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为敌人打开的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是枪眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗口里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着游击队的了望哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在紧张地开会呢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为中国的志愿队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天早晨来到了。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}